 understanding of life remains incompletely charted, he concludes, but the nature of its final destination is no longer an enigma.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Feb 2021) 7aSCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aCobb, Matthew.1 aDeBevoise, Malcolm.40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300142396423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300142396.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles